<br>
Settling in the shadow of one of the immense spires of stone, Tzann tried to contact Tevesh again, closing her eyes as she sent out her thoughts towards him.<br>
<br>
&quot;Tevesh?&quot; she sent.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yea', 'im h're,&quot; came his annoyed reply.<br>
<br>
