<br>
As he turned back around, Tzanntiel slid her arms around him, ignoring the chill of his armour.  Leaning up she nuzzled his chin.  &quot;Thank you, Tev.  You're wonderful.&quot;<br>
<br>
Tevesh chuckled deeply, slipping his arms around her, squeezing her tight.  &quot;I be s're ye w'll f'nd a w'y te m'ke it upta me,&quot; he growled, one of his hands sliding over her rump as he bent his head down to run his lips across her throat.<br>
<br>
