<br>
She had chosen him carefully, a few years ago, when she decided to make a base of operations for herself on Luclin.  He was awkward and very shy with women, and quite devoted to his studies.  She teased and seduced him, and eventually had him addicted to her blood as well.  Such a servant was very loyal, eager to take any risk to please their master.  She had ordered him a glass of wine before he arrived, and added some of her blood to the glass.  It wouldn't do to have such a nervous young man knowing what she was.<br>
<br>
