From the beginnings of her childhood, Cearyn was drawn to a part of Neriak that few approached.  It was no secret that the child had visions, dreams of what was to come, feelings of the people around her.  She had been claimed by the priesthood of Innoruuk from an early day.  But that was not to be her destiny.<br>
